channel.title: I was looking for two things
channel.description:
I can't seem to find funscap3 anywhere, you should know what im talking about.
And theres another server im trying to find, but haven't been able to find it. The second one, the only way i can try and describe what it is, is by this. The home was at clanwars, it was a PVP server, and you could spawn stuff in the quest tab i believe. And there was one quest, and you had to find titans around part of the map, then you had to fight the inadequacy to obtain a item i dont remember. If i remember right it was a 508 server...
If you can show me where i can download these servers ( with clients) i would be very greatful. Or if you know someone whos hosting these, it would be fun to play before my internet gets shut up in 10 days. Thanks in advance!
